      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio linee 23 e 24 di note operative     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "GL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      23                   to   v-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      v-alf                to   w-cnt-acc-sav-l23      .
