      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice errato : reimpostazione           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-yof-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tmo-orf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se a spaces : oltre                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tmo-orf        =    spaces
                     go to acc-tmo-orf-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su codice dipendenza                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tmo-orf-vld    not  = 02
