      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      08                   to   v-car                  .
           move      w-rig-dec-vpf        to   v-dec                  .
           add       w-rig-dec-prz        to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "G"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    to   v-lin                  .
           move      59                   to   v-pos                  .
