      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-acc-prz        to   w-det-prz-net-prz      .
           move      w-rig-per-scr (1)    to   w-det-prz-net-psc (1)  .
           move      w-rig-per-scr (2)    to   w-det-prz-net-psc (2)  .
