      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-exe-rca-pcm-tpm    =    01
                     go to acc-cod-mag-110
           else if   w-exe-rca-pcm-tpm    =    03
                     go to acc-cod-mag-130
           else      go to acc-cod-mag-999.
       acc-cod-mag-110.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
