      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cod-dpm-000      thru acc-cod-dpm-999        .
           go to     acc-cod-mag-400.
       acc-cod-mag-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cod-mag-600.
