      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcp-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cod-dcp-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valore a zero nom ammesso, a meno che non   *
      *                  * si sia in Up                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-exe-rca-pcm-cnm    not  = zero
                     go to acc-cod-dcp-600.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-cod-dcp-600
           else      go to acc-cod-dcp-100.
       acc-cod-dcp-600.
